cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SE, cs.DB

Reasoning: 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is the most likely category as the paper proposes an ontological representation and reasoning paradigm for interpretation of time-series signals using an incremental ASP solver. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper deals with interpreting complex sensor data using high level domain knowledge. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with inferring explanations for changes in the ambient air detected by the gas sensors. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper proposes a software solution for interpreting sensor data in a smart home environment. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is a possible category as the paper deals with representation and management of sensor data using an ontology.
